{
  "name": "agent-hook",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "Webhook 集中器",
  "category": "F",
  "number": 115,
  "pain_point": "Agent 回呼 webhook 雜亂",
  "commercial": "⚠️",
  "language": "Python",
  "dependencies": [
    "fastapi",
    "click",
    "rich"
  ],
  "agent_compatible": true,
  "mcp_ready": true,
  "intent_triggers": [
    "Agent 完成任務後的 webhook 怎麼統一管理？",
    "我有很多 Agent 各自有不同的 callback URL",
    "幫我做一個集中式的 webhook 接收器",
    "Agent 回呼通知四處散落很難維護",
    "如何讓所有 Agent 事件都進同一個 webhook 端點",
    "想要一個能接收並路由 Agent 事件的服務",
    "多個 Agent 的非同步回呼管理工具"
  ],
  "examples": [
    {
      "query": "啟動 webhook 集中器在 port 8090，接收所有 Agent 的完成事件",
      "params": {
        "action": "run",
        "port": "8090",
        "event_types": "task_complete,task_failed,task_started"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "設定當收到 payment_agent 回呼時轉發到 Slack 和資料庫",
      "params": {
        "action": "run",
        "source_agent": "payment_agent",
        "forward_to": "slack,database"
      }
    },
    {
      "query": "查看最近 24 小時的 webhook 接收記錄",
      "params": {
        "action": "run",
        "mode": "logs",
        "time_range": "24h"
      }
    }
  ],
  "params_schema": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "action": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "event_types": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "forward_to": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "mode": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "port": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "source_agent": {
        "type": "string"
      },
      "time_range": {
        "type": "string"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "action"
    ]
  },
  "license": "MIT"
}
